com.facebook.buck.core.cell

Interface NewCellPathResolver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultNewCellPathResolver

    public interface NewCellPathResolver
    The NewCellPathResolver maps between CanonicalCellNames and the absolute Path that they are rooted at.

    The behavior of NewCellPathResolver is the same for all cells in a build (unlike CellPathResolver).
